Job Responsibilities:

To conduct site measurement & inspection of external cable network to various target of planning building / area;
To liaise with internal and external parties such as contractor, engineers and technical staff for necessary planning and fitting out project;
Conduct site measurement and inspection of external cable network for planning and proposal of building / area;
Provide management services to monitor the work progress of the contractor for work implementation;
Prepare site drawing , site proposal, as-built drawings and update on system;
Prepare planning and proposal for major project and to liaise concerned internal and external parties for necessary implementation.

Job Requirements:

Diploma holder in IT or related discipline;
2-3 years relevant working experience;
Hands on experience in MS Office Applications ;
Holder of driving license will be an advantage;
Good analytical, PC / device trouble shooting, and problem solving skills;
Good interpersonal skill and a good team player;
Mature, dynamic, work independent and self-motivated;
Good spoken and written English and Cantonese, Mandarin a plus.

We offer competitive salary package and career development opportunity. Free company coach is provided.  Interested parties, please quote our reference number and apply with full resume, present and expected salary, by clicking “APPLY NOW”. 

